{"id":108,"date":"2022-03-16T22:04:11","date_gmt":"2022-03-16T13:04:11","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/?page_id=108"},"modified":"2023-07-21T19:04:26","modified_gmt":"2023-07-21T10:04:26","slug":"about","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/?page_id=108","title":{"rendered":"THE ORGANIZATION"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>INTRODUCTION<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">THEBLACKLABEL is the redefinition.<br>It\u2019s a collective of creatives bringing their vision to life.<br>It\u2019s developing talent in order to shift the culture.<br>It\u2019s a generation of risk takers pushing the outer boundaries of art<br>through bold experimentation and innovation. It\u2019s authenticity.<br>It\u2019s said that truth comes to light, but what\u2019s real happens in the dark.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">Welcome to THEBLACKLABEL.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">THEBLACKLABEL is a South Korean Entertainment Company founded in 2016 by TEDDY.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-3 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>FOUNDER<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">TEDDY<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">TEDDY is a visionary. He is the founder and architect behind THEBLACKLABEL.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">A pioneer in music with an illustrious 20+ year career as a songwriter and producer, TEDDY is credited as bringing Korean music into the new era. After debuting as an artist and producer, he went on to play an integral role in shaping the overall direction of the careers of global stars BIGBANG, G-DRAGON, 2NE1 and more. He is currently the Creative Director and Lead Producer of BLACKPINK &#8211; considered \u2018the biggest girl group in the world\u2019 with the Guinness World Record for the most subscribed YouTube music channel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">His longevity and consistent success creating new and innovative sounds has garnered him recognition and respect worldwide. TEDDY is known for his distinctive sound and has set trends not only in music, but also in the music video productions that has defined K-Pop during its rise to global stardom. He is undoubtedly one of the most influential figures of this era as a leader in the arts and has transcended into becoming a major player in the business of music and beyond. As a creative and an executive at THEBLACKLABEL, TEDDY unfolds his next chapter by bridging art, culture and entertainment, to illustrate a future that has yet to be seen.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"\/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-4 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><strong>SERVICES<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-5 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"376\" src=\"