TIVES<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\">TEDDY (CCO \/ PRODUCER \/ SONGWRITER)<br>KUSH (PRODUCER \/ SONGWRITER)<br>24 (PRODUCER \/ SONGWRITER)<br>VINCE (PRODUCER \/ SONGWRITER)<br>R.TEE (PRODUCER \/ SONGWRITER)<br>L\u00d8REN (PRODUCER \/ SONGWRITER)<br>DANNY CHUNG (SONGWRITER \/ A&amp;R)<br>GEE EUN (STYLING DIRECTOR \/ STYLIST)<br>SEAJUN (VISUAL DIRECTOR)<br>KHAN (PHOTOGRAPHER)<br>SOONHO (BUSINESS STRATEGY &amp; DEVELOPMENT \/ ARTIST MANAGEMENT)<br>MJ (BUSINESS STRATEGY &amp; DEVELOPMENT \/ A&amp;R)<br>RYU (ARTIST STRATEGY)<br>ENGINEERING TEAM<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:100px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-7 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-8 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>INTRODUCTION THEBLACKLABEL is the redefinition.It\u2019s a collective of creatives bringing their vision to life.It\u2019s developing talent in order to shift the culture.It\u2019s a generation of risk takers pushing the outer boundaries of artthrough bold experimentation and innovation. It\u2019s authenticity.It\u2019s said that truth comes to light, but what\u2019s real happens in the dark. Welcome to THEBLACKLABEL. THEBLACKLABEL is a South Korean [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/index.php?rest_route=\/wp\/v2\/pages\/108"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/index.php?res